  "A function to group tags. Accept a list of tags info, return
a tags tree like:

  (((\"group1\")
    ((\"subgroup1\")
     (\"tag1\" . tag-info))
    (\"tag2\" . tag-info))
   ((\"group2\")
    (\"tag3\" . tag-info)))

The group name set in a list to distinct with tags name.
"
  :group 'tags-tree
  :type 'function)

(defvar tags-tree-list nil "Alist for (FILE . TREE)")

